{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/offices-and-institutions/stk","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"STK ","meta_description":"Operation rules for vehicle inspection (STK).\r\n","content":{"processed":"<h2>Rules and recommendations</h2>\n<p><strong>STK (vehicle inspections) remains in operation</strong>. You can book an appointment for an inspection as driving without valid inspections is considered as minor offence even during the state of emergency. </p>\n<p><strong>It is allowed to leave the district in case of an essential visit of vehicle inspection</strong>, you can be accompanied by a close person or your relative. However, <strong>you must be able to prove the purpose of your travel</strong> across the district borders. To do so, we recommend to fulfil the appropriate <strong>form</strong> (<a href=\"https://www.vlada.cz/assets/media-centrum/aktualne/Formular_pro_cesty_mimo_okres_-_vzor.docx\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">word version</a>/<a href=\"https://www.vlada.cz/assets/media-centrum/aktualne/Formular_pro_cesty_mimo_okres_-_vzor.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">pdf version</a>) or <strong>affidavit</strong> (<a href=\"https://www.vlada.cz/assets/media-centrum/aktualne/Cestne_prohlaseni___vzor.docx\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">word version</a> /<a href=\"https://www.vlada.cz/assets/media-centrum/aktualne/Cestne_prohlaseni___vzor.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">pdf version</a>) defining the date, time, and purpose of your travel. You can print out the affidavit template or write it in hand. We also recommend taking the prove confirming the necessity of your travel (appointment invitation, etc.).</p>\n<p>Essential travel within the district is allowed, no certificate of your travel is needed in such a situation.</p>\n<p>Please be aware that <strong>since the 25th of February 2021, there is new regulation to wear at least an FPP2/KN95 respirator without exhalation vent</strong> or other face and mouth covering with at least 94% filtering ability. Other variants (scarfs, cloth face masks, etc.) will not be considered as sufficient protection starting from the 1st of March. </p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/offices-and-institutions/stk"},"changed":"2021-03-02T21:11:38+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-06T00:06:53+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://www.mdcr.cz/Media/Media-a-tiskove-zpravy/","title":"Details from the field of transport (only in Czech)"}],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":null,"situation_type":{"name":"Offices and institutions","path":{"alias":"/situations/offices-and-institutions"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"account_balance"}}},"measures":[{"title":"Movement restriction regulations","path":{"alias":"/measures/outdoor-activities/movement-restriction-regulations","langcode":"en"},"valid_from":"2021-03-01T00:00:00+01:00","valid_to":"2021-03-21T23:59:59+01:00","relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}]}}],"related_situations":[{"title":"Means of transport","path":{"alias":"/situations/hygiene/means-transport","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Public transport, taxi","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks-and-respirators/public-transport-taxi","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Blue zones","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people/blue-zones","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":null,"last_updated":"2021-03-02T22:15:00+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Offices and institutions","path":{"alias":"/situations/offices-and-institutions"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"account_balance"},"situation":[{"id":"87b78b06-9783-503c-a962-ea8a3817748e","title":"Operation of Public offices","path":{"alias":"/situations/offices-and-institutions/operation-public-offices"}},{"id":"6e525859-7f79-51ab-bb86-9798ec1b85c7","title":"ID exchange","path":{"alias":"/situations/offices-and-institutions/id-e